<span style="color: #909090;">**Others**</span>: [+ other_votes +]%

**Detailed results for each demographic**

Workers: <span style="color: #8B0000;">**CPGB**</span>: [+ workers_cpgb_display +]%, <span style="color: #E3000F;">**Labour**</span>: [+ workers_labour_display +]%, <span style="color: #0087DC;">**Tories**</span>: [+ workers_tories_display +]%, [? if liberals_exist: <span style="color: #DCCA4A;">**Liberals**</span>: [+ workers_liberals_display +]%, ?] <span style="color: #909090;">**Others**</span>: [+ workers_other_display +]%

New Middle Class: <span style="color: #8B0000;">**CPGB**</span>: [+ new_middle_cpgb_display +]%, <span style="color: #E3000F;">**Labour**</span>: [+ new_middle_labour_display +]%, <span style="color: #0087DC;">**Tories**</span>: [+ new_middle_tories_display +]%, [? if liberals_exist: <span style="color: #DCCA4A;">**Liberals**</span>: [+ new_middle_liberals_display +]%, ?] <span style="color: #909090;">**Others**</span>: [+ new_middle_other_display +]%

